room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Tropic Escape in Fort Myers
room_address: 4061 Bonita Beach Rd. Ste 203, Bonita Springs, FL 34134
room_description: As an ex-thief, you were recently hired to help stop a string of recent burglaries. You’re completing your rounds on your first night and things don’t seem right. The security system is engaged, everything is out of place, and an artifact is missing! You have 60 minutes to find the missing artifact and escape before the cops show up and arrest you for theft!
